Question Text: In just the past 12 months, what was the usual length of your menstrual cycle?
1= I have not had a menstrual period in the past 12 months
2= I have had at least one menstrual period in the past 12 months but the frequency of my period changed (such as it stopped, became irregular, or difficult to predict)
3= Too irregular to guess or using hormonal medication or device (such as an intrauterine device (IUD)) to control menstrual cycle
